i3
https://thevaluable.dev/i3-config-mouseless/
to enable i3 select i3 on top right menu before logging in

configure i3:
- ~/.config/i3/config for windows
- /etc/i3status.conf for the bar

to enable copy paste and wallpaper at startup, run this script:
#!/bin/bash
vmware-user #enable copy-paste
feh --bg-fill ~/Bureau/wallpaper.jpg
-----------------
i3 shortcuts

refresh i3:
win+shift+r

win+shift+a: close a window
win+r: resize mode (then use arrows)

win+enter: terminal
win+v+enter: new terminal (vertical split)
win+h+enter: new terminal (horizontal split)

win+d: dmenu

win+shift+space: floating window

win+num: create/navigate to num workspace
win+shift+num: move application to num workspace

-----------------
qterminal
ctrl+shift+t: new onglet
ctrl+tab: change onglet
ctrl+d or exit: quit onglet

ctrl+shift+w: quit qterminal
-----------------
kali
reboot: reboot
xfce4-settings-manager: settings
